data.description:
The house has 2 master bedroom suites (up & down stairs) with large closets, an office/nursery, and a private bath with shower and large jetted tub. The front room, living room, dinning room and kitchen share a 21' vaulted ceiling and the rest of the upstairs has 10' ceilings, bamboo hardwood floors and a beautiful gas fireplace. The house was built with 2×6 exterior walls, so they have 2 additional inches of insulation (the garage is also insulated), as well as, being sturdier than standard 2x4 construction...

The house conforms to current earthquake standards; the frame is strapped to the foundation and it has bearing walls (central walls reinforced with plywood to prevent ceiling colapse) upstairs and downstairs.

Downstairs is mostly finished; it has 8' cealings, large family room that is ready for a fireplace (gas, wood or combination) and is also ready for a 4th bathroom or a kitchette...

It has a large 2.5 car garage with an 8ft door. It will hold 2 cars/trucks and a couple of ATVs or motorcycles.

Both front and back yards are approx 100' × 35', there is also a large play house with its own deck and slide in the backyard (kids just love it)...
data.whatILove: The view, the big yard and gardens, the high ceilings, and the open floorplan. Recently carpeted and painted with brand new furnace...
